The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who want to become cybersecurity specialists. The program runs for 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Key topics include Windows, Linux, network administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by numerous institutions. The course offers flexibility in language, with options for English or Spanish. For more details, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop